data.title: Guatemala Top Destinations - Travelisimo
data.meta_description:
Escuintla is known for its natural beauty and unique beaches. It is located in the southern region, bordered to the north by Chimaltenango and Sacatepéquez, to the south by the Pacific Ocean, to the east by Santa Rosa and to the west by Suchitepéquez.

Playa El Paredón, Chulumar, Puerto Quetzal, Puerto San José and Sipacate are some of the most popular destinations in Escuintla, which enchant thousands of tourists every year with their beautiful scenery.
